cs.NE, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.NI 

The paper proposes a deep reinforcement learning approach for packet routing in computer networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper also involves the use of deep neural networks, which suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper deals with multi-agent systems, which could place it in cs.SY (Systems and Control) or cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture).
